\c 2
\s Rwiyo rwaHana
\p
\v 1 Zvino Hana wakanyengetera ndokuti: Moyo wangu unofara muna Jehovha\x + Ruk. 1.46-53. Map. 5.11. 9.2.\x*; runyanga rwangu rwakasimudzwa muna Jehovha\x + Map. 75.10. 89.17,24. 92.10. 112.9. 148.14.\x*; muromo wangu wakapamhamiswa pamusoro pevavengi vangu, nokuti ndinofara muruponeso rwenyu\x + Map. 9.14. 13.5. 20.5. 35.9.\x*.
\v 2 Hakuna mutsvene saJehovha\x + Eki. 15.11.\x*, nokuti hakuna \add umwe\add* kunze kwenyu\x + Det. 4.35.\x*; uye hakuna dombo \add rakaita\add* saMwari wedu\x + Det. 32.31.\x*.
\v 3 Musaramba muchitaura muchizvikudza-kudza, \add mu\add*chibudisa kuzvitutumadza pamuromo wenyu; nokuti Jehovha ndiMwari ane ruzivo rwakawanda, uye zviito zvinoyerwa naye\x + Mara. 3.13. Jud. 15.\x*.
\v 4 Uta hwevane simba hwakavhunika; uye vaigumburwa vakasunga zviuno nesimba\x + Map. 37.15. 46.9. 76.3.\x*.
\v 5 Vaiva vakaguta vakazviitisa vabati nekuda kwechingwa, uye vaiva nenzara havachaka\add daro,\x + Ruk. 1.53. Map. 34.10.\x*\add* kusvika vaiva mhanje vabereka vanomwe\x + Map. 68.6. 113.9. Isa. 54.1.\x*, neane vana vazhinji apera simba\x + Jer. 15.9.\x*.
\v 6 Jehovha anouraya uye anoraramisa; anoburusira kubwiro, uye anokwidza\x + Det. 32.39.\x*.
\v 7 Jehovha anopa urombo, uye anofumisa\x + Eki. 15.9. Job. 1.21.\x*; anoderedza, anokwiridzirawo\x + Map. 75.7. Job. 5.11.\x*.
\v 8 Anosimudza murombo paguruva, anosimudza anoshaiwa kubva mudurunhuru\x + Map. 113.7,8. Ruk. 1.52. Dhan. 4.17.\x*, kuti a\add va\add*garise pamwe nemachinda, uye anovagarisa nhaka yechigaro chekutonga cherukudzo\x + Job. 36.7.\x*. Nokuti mbiru dzenyika ndedzaJehovha, uye wakaisa nyika pamusoro padzo\x + Job. 38.4,5,6. Map. 24.2. 102.25. 104.5.\x*.
\v 9 Achachengeta tsoka dzevatsvene vake\x + Map. 121.3. Zvir. 3.26. Map. 91.11.\x*, asi vakaipa vachanyaradzwa murima; nokuti munhu haangakundi nesimba.
\v 10 Vanorwa naJehovha vachapwanyiwa\x + Map. 2.9.\x*; achatinhira pamusoro pavo ari kumatenga\x + 7.10. Map. 18.13. 2 Sam. 22.14.\x*; Jehovha achatonga migumo yenyika; uye achapa simba kuna mambo wake\x + Map. 96.10,13. 98.9.\x*, nekusimudzira runyanga rwemuzodzwa wake\x + 2.1.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino Erikana wakaenda kuRama kumba kwake\x + 1.19.\x*. Asi mukomana waishumira Jehovha pamberi pemupristi Eri\x + 2.18. 3.1.\x*.
\s Kutadza kwevana vaEri
\p
\v 12 Zvino vanakomana vaEri vaiva vana vaBheriari\x + 1.3. Det. 13.13.\x*; havana kuziva Jehovha\x + Vato. 2.10.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino tsika yevapristi pavanhu yaiva \add iyi\add*: Kana ani nani akapa chibairo, muranda wemupristi waiuya nyama ichiri kubikwa ane chibayiso chenyama chemeno matatu muruoko rwake;
\v 14 ndokukanda mugango kana muhadyana kana mugate resimbi kana muhari; chose chibayiso chenyama chachabudisa mupristi waizvitorera\x + Rev. 7.30-34. Det. 18.3.\x*. Vakaita saizvozvo kuna Israeri wose waisvikapo paShiro.
\v 15 Zvino vasati vapisa mafuta, muranda wemupristi waiuya, ndokuti kumunhu anobaira: Ndipe nyama yekugochera mupristi; nokuti haangatori kwauri nyama yakabikwa, asi mbishi\x + Rev. 3.3,4,5,16. 7.23,25,31.\x*.
\v 16 Kana munhu uyo akati kwaari: Ngavapise zvekupisa mafuta ikozvino, ugozozvitorera moyo wako sezvaunoda; iye ndokuti kwaari: Haiwa, \add ndi\add*pe ikozvino; kana zvisina kudaro ndichatora nechisimba.
\v 17 Naizvozvo chivi chemajaya chakava chikuru kwazvo pamberi paJehovha\x + Gen.. 6.11.\x*, nokuti vanhu vakazvidza chipo chaJehovha\x + Mara. 2.8.\x*.
\p
\v 18 Asi Samueri waishumira pamberi paJehovha, ari mukomana\x + 2.11.\x* akasunga chiuno neefodhi* yemucheka\x + Eki. 28.4. 2 Sam. 6.14. 1 Makor. 15.27. Rev. 6.10.\x*.
\v 19 Uye mai vake vakamuitira nguvo diki, ndokuiunza kwaari gore negore pakukwira kwavo nemurume wavo kuzobaira chibairo chegore\x + 1.3.\x*.
\p
\v 20 Zvino Eri wakaropafadza Erikana nemukadzi wake, ndokuti: Jehovha ngaakupe mbeu nemukadzi uyu panzvimbo yechikumbiro chakakumbirwa kuna Jehovha. Zvino vakaenda kunzvimbo yake\x + Num.. 6.23. Gen.. 14.19.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino Jehovha wakashanyira Hana, iye ndokubata mimba, ndokubereka vanakomana vatatu nevanasikana vaviri\x + Gen.. 21.1.\x*. Mukomana Samueri ndokukura muna Jehovha\x + 2.26. Vato. 13.24.\x*.
\p
\v 22 Zvino Eri waiva akwegura kwazvo, ndokunzwa zvose vanakomana vake zvavaiitira Israeri wose\x + 2.13-16.\x*, uye kuti vairara nevakadzi vaiungana pamukova wetende rekusangana.
\v 23 Ndokuti kwavari: Munoitirei zvinhu zvakadai? Nokuti ndinonzwa nevanhu ava vose zviito zvenyu zvakaipa.
\v 24 Kwete, vanakomana vangu; nokuti harwusi runyerekupe rwakanaka rwandinonzwa; moita vanhu vaJehovha kuti vatsauke.
\v 25 Kana munhu akatadzira umwe, vatongi vachamutonga\x + Eki. 21.6. 22.8,9,28. Eki. 12.12.\x*; asi kana munhu akatadzira Jehovha, ndiani achamunyengeterera? Asi havana kuteerera inzwi rababa vavo, nokuti Jehovha waida kuvauraya\x + Josh. 11.20. Zvir. 15.10.\x*.
\v 26 Zvino mukomana Samueri wakaenderera mberi achikura\x + 2.21. Gen.. 26.13. 2 Makor. 17.12.\x*, ndokudikanwa zvose kuna Jehovha nekuvanhu\x + Ruk. 2.52. Zvir. 3.4. Mab. 24.16. VaRom. 14.18.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Zvino kwakasvika munhu waMwari kuna Eri\x + 1 Madz. 13.1. Vato. 13.6.\x*, ndokuti kwaari: Ndizvo zvinoreva Jehovha: Handina kuzviratidza kwazvo here kuimba yababa vako vachiri muEgipita muimba yaFarao\x + Eki. 4.14,27.\x*?
\v 28 Ndakamusarudza here kubva pamarudzi ose aIsraeri kuva mupristi kwandiri\x + Eki. 28.1-4. Num.. 18.1,7.\x*, akwire kuaritari yangu kupisa zvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira, kupfeka efodhi pamberi pangu\x + 14.3. 22.18.\x*? Ndakapa imba yababa vako zvipo zvemoto zvose zvevana vaIsraeri here\x + Rev. 2.3,10. 6.16. 7.7,8,34. 10.14,15. Num.. 5.9,10. 18.8-19.\x*?
\v 29 Sei muchikava chibairo changu nechipo changu\x + Det. 32.15.\x*, zvandakaraira mumba \add mangu\x + 2.32. Det. 26.15. 33.27. 1 Makor. 4.41. Map. 26.8. 68.5. Det. 12.5,6.\x*\add*, uye munoremekedza vanakomana vako kukunda ini, muchizvikodza nezvakanakisisa zvezvipo zvose zvaIsraeri, vanhu vangu?
\v 30 Naizvozvo Jehovha Mwari waIsraeri anoti: Ndakati zvirokwazvo: Imba yako neimba yababa vako dzichafamba pamberi pangu nekusingaperi\x + Eki. 27.21. 29.5.\x*; asi ikozvino anoti Jehovha: Ngazvive kure neni\x + Jer. 18.9,10.\x*, nokuti vanondikudza ndichavakudza\x + Map. 91.14.\x*, uye vanondizvidza ndichavashoora\x + Mara. 2.9.\x*.
\v 31 Tarira, mazuva anouya, andichagura ruoko rwako, neruoko rweveimba yababa vako, kusava nemutana paimba yako\x + 4.11,18,20. 22.18. 1 Madz. 2.27.\x*.
\v 32 Zvino uchaona kutambudzika kweimba \add yangu\add*, pane zvose zvaanenge aita zvakanakira Israeri; uye hapangavi nemutana paimba yako mazuva ose\x + 2.33. Zek. 8.4.\x*.
\v 33 Zvino uyo wekwako wandisingazoguri abve paaritari yangu, achava wekupedza meso ako, nekurwadzisa moyo wako; nekuwanda kwose kweimba yako kuchafa kuchiri pakuva varume.
\v 34 Zvino ichi chichava chiratidzo kwauri chezvichauya kuvanakomana vako vaviri kuna Hofini naPinehasi\x + 1 Madz. 13.3.\x*: Vachafa vari vaviri nezuva rimwe\x + 4.11.\x*.
\v 35 Zvino ndichazvimutsira mupristi wakatendeka; achaita sezviri pamoyo wangu nemurangariro wangu\x + 1 Madz. 2.35.\x*; uye ndichamuvakira imba yakasimba\x + 25.28. 1 Madz. 11.38. 2 Sam. 7.11,27.\x*, uye achafamba pamberi pemuzodzwa wangu mazuva ose\x + 2 Sam. 22.51. Map. 18.50. Map. 89.20.\x*.
\v 36 Zvino zvichaitika, umwe neumwe achasara paimba yako achauya agofugama kwaari nekuda kwemuripo wesirivha nechimedu chechingwa, uye achati: Ndibatisei henyu pane rimwe remabasa eupristi kuti ndidye chimedu chechingwa\x + 10.3. Eki. 29.23. Vato. 8.5. Zvir. 6.26.\x*.